metadata.description: The Hungover Apes Party Club is a collection of 7,777 unique Hungover Apes NFTs living on the Ethereum blockchain. Holders will be granted access to members-only benefits including free merch, exclusive events such as NFT claims, raffles, community giveaways, and more. Future areas and perks will be unlocked by the community through roadmap activation.
metadata.name: Hungover Ape #1 - Legendary
